data.meta_description:
15 likes, 1 comments - beyondthereturn on March 20, 2024: "For women's month, @umi.foundation is having its 'A Lady With A Dream Conference that will bring women together in sharing valuable insights and empowering each other.

Take a look at all the phenomenal women who will be speaking at the event. It's an opportunity to bring Ghanaians and the diaspora together in unity.

The UMI Foundation is a nonprofit organisation that has a focus on inspiring people to help their communities. They raise awareness about important issues and support initiatives in health, education, climate change, and reducing poverty.
This aligns with the Give Back Ghana Pillar of the Beyond the Return initiative that works towards finding ways to give back to our community. 

The conference is FREE to attend. You only have to tap the link in bio to register.

Venue: M.T Addico Conference Hall, Ghana
Shipper's Authority
Time: 9:00 AM
Date: March 23, 2024

See you there! 

_______________

Beyond the Return is a 10-year initiative with the theme, 'A decade of African Renaissance'

The office operates under  @ghanatourismauthority and has a foundation of 7 pillars.
>Experience Ghana
>Celebrate Ghana
>Diaspora Pathways to Ghana
>Invest in Ghana
>Give Back Ghana
>Brand Ghana
>Promote Pan African Heritage & Innovation

Learn more on our website www.beyondthereturngh.com 

#beyondthereturn #Ghana #celebrateGhana #Africa #culture #diaspora".
